content: I'm in the 32801 zip code, and I usually shop at Walmart, Target, and Costco. I'm open to buying in bulk if it's a good deal, but I also want to make sure I'm not overspending. I don't have a specific brand preference for toilet paper, but for laundry detergent, I like Tide. Oh, and by the way, I've been using coupons a lot more frequently lately - I started about two months ago, and it's been making a big difference in my grocery bills.
